data.description: This property offers quiet, serene surroundings but only minutes to downtown Nashville.  Located in Davidson County but has an Ashland City mailing address.  Very rustic home sitting on 4.82 acres (per tax card).  The property also has a 2nd livable/studio on the land.  Currently being used as a music studio, but with the extra  studio building there is the possibility for another 1200 sf of living space, with 2 bedrooms, living area, bathroom and kitchen. Property is on well/spring, but city water is available.  Perfect for Air Bnb, In-laws, adult children, etc.  Property previously had horses.  Older barn and some fencing.  Property is being sold AS IS.
